import Home from "../src/pages/index"
import {Routes,Route} from "react-router-dom"
import Dashboard from "../src/pages/index"
function App() {
  return <>
  <Routes>
    <Route path="/" element={<Dashboard content={<Home />} />}></Route>
    <Route path="/detay" element={<Home/>}></Route>
  </Routes>
  </>
}

export default App;
